code: public void setComparator(Comparator<E> comparator) {     this.comparator = comparator. }

@Override public PriorityBlockingQueue<E> create() {     return comparator == null ? new PriorityBlockingQueue<>() : // PriorityQueue as a default capacity of 11     new PriorityBlockingQueue<>(11, comparator). }
@Override public PriorityBlockingQueue<E> create(int capacity) {     return comparator == null ? new PriorityBlockingQueue<>(capacity) : new PriorityBlockingQueue<>(capacity, comparator). }
